name: Fauna Flowers 01 - Onça Flower
description:
Sometimes it exhales magical fragrance, sometimes it purrs. Elegance that comes directly from the dense forests, this flower mixes magnificence and an iconic print. No need to fear this kitten!

Fauna Flowers is a collection made of animals mixed with plants in a new kind of magical possibilities. Discover this world where flowers can be a magnificent diversity of beautiful and unique creatures.
